<sent type="title" lang="chi" page="01a" n="1">詩經諺解 卷之八</sent>
<sent type="title3" lang="chi" page="01a" n="2">豳</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="3">七月流火ᅵ어든 九月授衣노니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="3">七月에 火ᅵ 流거든 九月에 衣를 授니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a-01b" n="4">一之日觱發고 二之日栗烈니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a-01b" n="4">一之日에 觱發고 二日에 栗烈니</sent><!--觱^發-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="1">無衣無褐이면 何以卒歲리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="1">衣 업고 褐이 업면 엇디  歲 卒리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="2">三之日于耜ᅵ오 四之日擧趾어든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="2">三之日에 가 耜고 四之日에 趾를 擧거든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="3">同我婦子야 饁彼南畝커든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="3">우리 婦子 同야 뎌 南畝애 饁거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="4">田畯至喜니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="4">田畯이 至야 喜니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="1">七月流火ᅵ어든 九月授衣니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="1">七月에 火ᅵ 流거든 九月에 衣 授니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="2">春日載陽야 有鳴倉庚이어든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="2">春日이 비로소 陽야 倉庚이 鳴거든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="3">女執懿筐야 遵彼微行야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="3">女ᅵ 懿 筐을 執야 뎌 微行을 遵야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="4">爰求柔桑며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="4">이에 柔桑을 求며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="5">春日遲遲어든 采蘩祁祁니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="5">春日이 遲遲거든 蘩을 采홈을 祁祁히 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="6">女心傷悲ᅵ여 殆及公子同歸로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="6">女의 이 傷悲홈이여  公子로 가지로 歸리로다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="1">七月流火ᅵ어든 八月萑葦니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="1">七月에 火ᅵ 流거든 八月에 萑葦를 니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="2">蠶月條桑이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="2">蠶月에 條桑논디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="3">取彼斧斨야 以伐遠揚이오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="3">뎌 斧斨을 取야  遠揚을 伐고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="4">猗彼女桑이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="4">뎌 女桑을 猗리라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="1">七月鳴鵙이어든 八月載績니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="1">七月에 鵙이 鳴거든 八月에 곧 績니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="2">載玄載黃야 我朱孔陽이어든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="2">곧 玄며 곧 黃야 우리 朱ᅵ 심히 陽거든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="3">爲公子裳니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="3">公子의 裳을 니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="1">四月秀葽ᅵ어든 五月鳴蜩ᅵ며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="1">四月에 葽ᅵ 秀거든 五月에 蜩ᅵ 鳴며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="2">八月其穫이어든 十月隕蘀이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="2">八月에 그 穫거든 十月에 隕며 蘀니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="3">一之日于貉야 取彼狐貍야 爲公子裘고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="3">一之日에 가 貉야 뎌 狐와 狸 取야 公子의 裘 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="4">二之日其同야 載纘武功야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="4">二之日에 그 同야 곧 武功을 纘야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="5">言私其豵이오 獻豣于公니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="5">그 豵을 私고 豣을 公애 獻니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="1">五月斯螽動股ᅵ오 六月莎鷄振羽ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="1">五月에 斯螽이 股 動고 六月에 莎鷄羽 振고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="2">七月在野ᅵ오 八月在宇ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="2">七月에 野애 잇고 八月에 宇에 잇고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="3">九月在戶ᅵ오 十月蟋蟀이 入我牀下니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="3">九月에 戶애 잇고 十月에 蟋蟀이 우리 牀 아래 드니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a-04b" n="4">穹窒熏鼠며 塞向墐戶고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a-04b" n="4">穹을 窒며 鼠 熏며 向을 塞며 戶 墐고</sent><!--墐^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="1">嗟我婦子아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="1">嗟홉다 우리 婦子아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="2">曰爲改歲어니 入此室處ᅵ어다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="2">오 歲ᅵ 改커니 이 室에 드러 處홀띠어다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="3">六月食鬱及薁며 七月亨葵及菽며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="3">六月에 鬱과 밋 薁을 머그며 七月에 葵와 밋 菽을 亨며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b-05a" n="4">八月剝棗며 十月穫稻야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b-05a" n="4">八月에 棗 剝며 十月에 稻 穫야</sent><!--에 ^ 棗-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="1">爲此春酒야 以介眉壽니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="1">이 春酒 야  眉壽 介니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="2">七月食瓜며 八月斷壺며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="2">七月에 瓜 食며 八月에 壺 斷며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="3">九月叔苴며 采荼薪樗야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="3">九月에 苴 叔며 荼 采며 樗 薪야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="4">食我農夫니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="4">우리 農夫 食니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="1">九月築場圃ᅵ오 十月納禾稼니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1">九月에 場을 圃애 築고 十月에 禾稼 納니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="2">黍稷重穋과 禾麻菽麥이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="2">黍와 稷이 重며 穋니과 禾와 麻와 菽과 麥이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="3">嗟我農夫아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="3">嗟홉다 우리 農夫아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="4">我稼旣同이어니 上入執宮功이니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="4">우리 稼ᅵ 이믜 同거니 上入야 宮功을 執띠니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="5">晝爾于茅ᅵ오 宵爾索綯야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="5">나 네가 茅고 밤의 네 綯 索야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="6">亟其乘屋이오 其始播百穀이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="6">리 그 屋애 乘고 그 비로소 百穀을 播홀띠니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="1">二之日鑿冰沖沖야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">二之日에 冰을 鑿홈을 冲冲히 야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="2">三之日納于凌陰니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">三之日에 凌陰에 納니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a-06b" n="3">四之日其蚤애 獻羔祭韭니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a-06b" n="3">四之日 그 蚤애 羔 獻고 韭로 祭니라</sent><!--^고-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="1">九月肅霜이어든 十月滌場고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">九月에 肅야 霜거든 十月에 場을 滌고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="2">朋酒斯饗야 曰殺羔羊야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="2">朋酒로 이예 饗야 羔와 羊을 殺야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="3">躋彼公堂야 稱彼兕觥니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">뎌 公堂의 躋야 뎌 兕觥을 稱니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="4">萬壽無疆이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="4">萬壽야 疆이 업리로다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="06b" n="5">七月 八章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="1">鴟鴞鴟鴞아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="1">鴟鴞아 鴟鴞아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="2">旣取我子ᅵ어니 無毁我室이어다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="2">이믜 내 子 取여니 내 室을 毁티 마롤띠어다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="3">恩斯勤斯야 鬻子之閔斯ᅵ라니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="3">恩며 勤야 子 鬻홈이 閔다니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="4">迨天之未陰雨야 徹彼桑土야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="4">天의 陰雨티 아닌 저글 믿처 뎌 桑土 撤야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="5">椆繆牖戶ᅵ면 今女下民이 或敢侮予아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="5">牖와 戶 綢繆면 이제 너 下民이 或 敢히 나 侮랴</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="1">予手拮据야 予所捋荼ᅵ며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="1">내 手ᅵ 拮据야 내 荼 捋논 배며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="2">予所蓄租ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="2">내 蓄며 租논 배라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="3">予口卒瘏 曰予未有室家ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="3">내 口ᅵ 다 瘏홈은 내 室家 두디 몯여실니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="1">予羽譙譙며 予尾翛翛야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="1">내 羽ᅵ 譙譙며 내 尾ᅵ 翛翛야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="2">予室翹翹ᅵ어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="2">내 室이 翹翹거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="3">風雨所漂搖ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="3">風雨ᅵ 漂搖 배라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="4">予維音嘵嘵호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="4">내 音을 哮哮히 호라</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="08a" n="5">鴟鴞 四章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="1">我徂東山야 慆慆不歸호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="1">내 東山의 가 慆慆히 歸티 몯호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="2">我來自東일 零雨其濛이리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="2">내 옴을 東으로브터  零 雨ᅵ 그 濛더라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="3">我東曰歸예 我心西悲호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="3">東애셔 歸 제 내 이 西로 悲호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="4">制彼裳衣야 勿士行枚로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="4">뎌 裳衣 制야 行枚 士티 마롤띠로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="5">蜎蜎者蠋이여 烝在桑野ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="5">蜎蜎 蠋이여 桑野의 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="6">敦彼獨宿이여 亦在車下ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="6">敦히 뎌 獨宿 이여  車下의 잇도다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="1">我徂東山야 慆慆不歸호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="1">내 東山의 가 慆慆히 歸티 몯호라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="2">我來自東일 零雨其濛이러라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="2">내 옴을 東으로브터  零 雨ᅵ 그 濛더라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="3">果臝之實이 亦施于宇ᅵ며</sent>
